@inject AdminBlockService BlockService
@inject IHttpService Http
@using Contracts.Admin

<div class="form-group">
    <label class="form-label">@T("Image")</label>
    @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(_imageUrl))
    {
        <div style="margin-bottom:.75rem">
            <img src="@_imageUrl"
                 style="max-height:160px;border-radius:6px;
            border:1px solid var(--border)" />
            <button class="btn-admin btn-ghost" style="margin-left:.5rem"
                    @onclick="() => _imageUrl = null">
                <i class="fas fa-times"></i> @T("Remove")
            </button>
        </div>
    }
    <div style="display:flex;gap:.5rem;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <InputFile id="image-block-upload"
                   OnChange="OnFileSelected"
                   accept="image/*"
                   style="display:none" />
        <label class="btn-admin btn-ghost" for="image-block-upload">
            <i class="fas fa-image"></i> @T("UploadNew")
        </label>
        <button type="button" class="btn-admin btn-ghost" @onclick="OpenResourcePicker">
            <i class="fas fa-photo-film"></i> @T("ChooseFromResourceLibrary")
        </button>
    </div>
    <div class="form-hint">@T("UploadImageHint")</div>
</div>

<ResourcePickerModal Open="_resourcePickerOpen"
                     Kind="image"
                     ResourceSelected="SelectResourceImage"
                     Closed="CloseResourcePicker" />

<div class="form-group">
    <label class="form-label">@T("AltText")</label>
    <LangField @bind-Value="_altText"
               Languages="Languages"
               NullText="@T("AltTextHint")" />
</div>

<div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:.75rem">
    <button class="btn-admin btn-primary" @onclick="Save" disabled="@_saving">
        <i class="fas fa-save"></i> @(_saving ? T("Saving") : T("Save"))
    </button>
</div>

@code {
    [Parameter] public BlockModel Block { get; set; } = new();
    [Parameter] public string PageId { get; set; } = string.Empty;
    [Parameter] public string SectionId { get; set; } = string.Empty;
    [Parameter] public List<string> Languages { get; set; } = new() { "en" };
    [Parameter] public EventCallback OnSaved { get; set; }
    [CascadingParameter(Name = "AdminLanguage")] public string AdminLanguage { get; set; } = "en";

    private string? _imageUrl;
    private Dictionary<string, string> _altText = new();
    private bool _saving;
    private bool _resourcePickerOpen;
    private string T(string key) => AdminUiLocalizer.T(key, AdminLanguage);

    protected override void OnParametersSet()
    {
        _imageUrl = Block.ImageUrl;
        _altText = new(Block.AltText ?? new());
    }

    private async Task OnFileSelected(InputFileChangeEventArgs e)
    {
        var file = e.File;
        if (file.Size > 5 * 1024 * 1024) return;

        var res = await Http.PostFileAsync<AssetUploadModel>("api/admin/assets/upload?folder=image-blocks", file, maxBytes: 5 * 1024 * 1024);
        if (res.Success && res.Data is not null)
        {
            _imageUrl = res.Data.Url;
            Http.Toast("Image uploaded.", res.StatusCode);
        }
        else
        {
            Http.Toast(res.Message ?? "Image upload failed.", res.StatusCode);
        }
    }

    private void OpenResourcePicker()
    {
        _resourcePickerOpen = true;
    }

    private void CloseResourcePicker()
    {
        _resourcePickerOpen = false;
    }

    private void SelectResourceImage(ManagedResourceModel resource)
    {
        _imageUrl = resource.Url;
        if (_altText.Count == 0 || !_altText.Values.Any(value => !string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(value)))
            _altText = new(resource.Name);
    }

    private async Task Save()
    {
        _saving = true;
        try
        {
            var res = await BlockService.UpdateAsync(PageId, SectionId, Block.Id, new ImageBlockUpdateDto
            {
                ImageUrl = _imageUrl,
                AltText = _altText,
                Visible = Block.Visible
            });
            Http.Toast(res.Message, res.StatusCode);
            if (res.Success) await OnSaved.InvokeAsync();
        }
        finally
        {
            _saving = false;
        }
    }
}
